title: Ultimate 2BR/2BA Condo -  250 Santa Fe Terrace 212
posting_body: ['Capture The Charm, Love The Space, Live The Location', 'Truly exceptional, the custom-designed floor plan features a character-filled interior and comes complete with relaxed living spaces.', 'This home is built with a balcony just off the living room, making this a great spot for enjoying a morning cup of coffee.', 'Wake up refreshed in the spacious main bedroom that boasts an ensuite bathroom and a large closet.', 'Low-maintenance and simple, the main bathroom benefits from a rainshower, soaking tub, and double sinks.', 'Other amenities include window air-conditioning, central heating, a community pool, and in-unit laundry.', ' Reap the benefits of neighborhood living in a desirable part of Santa Clara County.', 'Experience everything that this wonderful community offers.', 'An easy commute, thanks to freeway and bus stops only minutes away.', 'A rare opportunity.', 'Want to know more?', 'Call today..', '** Tenant pays for electricity and cable.', '** Tenant(s) will be responsible for following any HOA-mandated “Rules & Responsibilities” and “Covenants, Conditions & Restrictions.”', '**', '** Tenant is responsible for any HOA Move in/Move out fees if applicable**', '** Security Deposit is equal to 1x the monthly rent based upon approved credit.', '(NOTE: In WA, security deposits have a maximum cap at 1x rent.', 'Allowed to have a separate and additional refundable Pet Damage Deposit equal to 25% of the monthly rent)', '**', 'If you are interested in applying, please email', 'show contact info', 'or text', 'show contact info', 'to request an application.', 'Please note that applications are reviewed in the order received and application fees are not refundable.', '**']
